    "description": "<strong>星际裂谷</strong>是一款开放世界战舰模拟游戏，着重于星舰建设及多人互动。玩家可使用私人定制的星舰探索并征服星系。宇宙虽浩瀚无垠，但你不是一个人，其他玩家可加入你的空勤组，给予你帮助；或建立属于他们自己的敌对舰队，与你在星际中一争高下。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/4d7d88c9374f75b2171b82b313b487cd.webp?t=1725029706\" width=640 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/f537d7a99a2ff08581a8aff709e57c0e.poster.avif?t=1725029706\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/f537d7a99a2ff08581a8aff709e57c0e.webm?t=1725029706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/f537d7a99a2ff08581a8aff709e57c0e.mp4?t=1725029706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>准备好</strong>将飞船打造成你的家园，同时探索星系！玩家可根据个人喜好，在星舰编辑器中对星舰进行设计，选择范围囊括小型探索舰艇、大型货物运输机，甚至是巨型战舰。玩家可以在编辑器中通过一砖一瓦，从内到外建造自己的星舰。如果想要快速进行游戏，玩家可以选择工作坊内他人建造的星舰，或上传自己的蓝图。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/7f534968d3598db0577e16e124657ca0.webp?t=1725029706\" width=640 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/9c8a74f24301178a4b6af3165b1bea0b.poster.avif?t=1725029706\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/9c8a74f24301178a4b6af3165b1bea0b.webm?t=1725029706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/9c8a74f24301178a4b6af3165b1bea0b.mp4?t=1725029706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>即便是独自畅玩，<strong>星系</strong>也并不总是那么太平。陌生的时空裂谷已被开启，名为斯克里尔的外来生物种族打开了通往世界的大门。不加以留意的话，它们将占领太阳系，践踏你的心血。你可以选择孤身奋战，也可以寻求好友的帮助，一起组建星舰。但并非所有飞行员都是正义的，海盗和敌方舰队也会袭击你的星舰，掠夺你的货物。与他们进行正面交锋，或者以黑客技术侵入他们的舰艇，主动出击，近距离射击。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/05d68b3150a7c2489f3228835f9bba4c.webp?t=1725029706\" width=640 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/75c169f5982667228b98265d2474e0bb.poster.avif?t=1725029706\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/75c169f5982667228b98265d2474e0bb.webm?t=1725029706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/75c169f5982667228b98265d2474e0bb.mp4?t=1725029706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>时空裂谷中的<strong>经济</strong>运转依靠的是星系中可收集的资源。巨大的小行星装满了价值不菲的矿石矿物，环绕着行星和太阳系运行。你可以启动资源提取器，也可以派出一波开采无人机为你效力。探访罗吉公司银河贸易网络，或是在为搁浅的飞行员送上燃料时狠狠剥削他们。使用 ACTR（自动货物转移中继装置）建造自动化生产线，建立属于自己的商店，与其他玩家或贸易无人机进行交易。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/f44fd0e7c688607f9c387768d6df9f5e.webp?t=1725029706\" width=640 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/44b12991b331f5e98aff3cbd4baee4b0.poster.avif?t=1725029706\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/44b12991b331f5e98aff3cbd4baee4b0.webm?t=1725029706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/363360/extras/44b12991b331f5e98aff3cbd4baee4b0.mp4?t=1725029706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>在</strong>选择结盟帮派后，你就可以尽情探索宇宙了。使用时空裂谷发动机来打开空间裂缝，将你带到全新的星系，探索星系将帮助你绘制出星系地图，并标注能够生产你所需要的特殊资源的星系位置。帮助渴望扩大影响力的集团和帮派建立新的贸易站、安防战和安防区。通过完成任务获得尤利特币，或在众多星系中寻找有利可图的交易机会。",
